            "component": "TextGroup",
            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Text",
                "content": "# **Friendship super skills**\n\nIn the last challenge you learned to master the skill of taking a breathing pause – a simple little pause that helps you be less reactive.\n\nNow we’ll build on it with two more skills – awareness and allowing."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "component": "ButtonGroup",
            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Button",
                "sectionId": "2",
                "conversationId": "relationship-aoa-2",
                "content": "Go on"
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "id": "1",
        "alias": "1",
        "type": "defaultSection"
      },
      {
        "id": "2",
        "alias": "2",
        "content": [
          {
            "component": "TextGroup",
            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Text",
                "content": "Think of awareness and allowing as skills for life. Along with the breathing pause, these skills will help you with your friendships. \n\nIt will give you a space to separate your own thoughts from truths and go about with important actions even in the presence of difficult feelings."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "component": "ButtonGroup",
            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Button",
                "content": "Continue",
                "sectionId": "3",
                "conversationId": "relationship-aoa-2"
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "type": "defaultSection"
      },
      {
        "id": "3",
        "alias": "3",
        "content": [
          {
            "component": "TextGroup",
            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Text",
                "content": "**Awareness** is:\n\nNoticing what is happening in your body\n\nNoticing what sensations you are experiencing"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "component": "ButtonGroup",
            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Button",
                "content": "Next",
                "sectionId": "4",
                "conversationId": "relationship-aoa-2"
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "type": "defaultSection"
      },
      {
        "id": "4",
        "alias": "4",
        "content": [
          {
            "component": "TextGroup",
            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Text",
                "content": "**Allowing is:**\n\nSeeing thoughts and feelings as coming and going without grabbing or judging them\n\nSeeing thoughts and feelings as messengers, knowing they are not dangerous like knives or guns"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "component": "ButtonGroup",
            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Button",
                "content": "Got it",
                "sectionId": "5",
                "conversationId": "relationship-aoa-2"
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "type": "defaultSection"
      },
      {
        "id": "5",
        "alias": "5",
        "content": [
          {
            "component": "TextGroup",
            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Text",
                "content": "Becoming aware of and allowing your inner sensations are two great skills in helping with friendships. How? Well, you’ll end up less likely to say and do things you will regret later on.\n\nGet ready for a two minute practice to get you on your way."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "component": "ButtonGroup",
            "content": [
              {
                "component": "NextConversationButton",
                "content": "I'm ready",
                "conversationId": "relationships-aoa-3",
                "sectionId": "root"
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "type": "defaultSection"
      }
    ]
  },
  "sv": {
    "type": "lesson",
